<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>My Portfolio</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      height: 90vh;
      background: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/8622843/pexels-photo-8622843.jpeg') no-repeat center center/cover;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero-overlay h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero-overlay p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
    }
.project{
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 3rem;
}
.section {
  padding: 60px 20px;
  background-color: #f5f5f5;
  display: inline;
  justify-content: flex-end;
}

.container {
  padding-top: 30px;
  padding-right: 80px;
  max-width: 1400px;
  text-align: left;
}

.container h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: #058f38;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.container p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: black;
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .section {
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .container p {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
}
 
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <h1>portfolio</h1>
      <p>View the range of projects completed by Nextloop Technologies. We have provided 
        assistance to a wide range of firms in various industries and locations across the 
        globe, from small startups to large corporations. This demonstrates our exceptional
         ability to generate fresh concepts and tailor solutions to the specific needs of each client. 
         So, if you're interested in learning more about what Nextloop can accomplish for your company, 
         have a look at our portfolios!</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  
    <div class="project">
      <h2>Shower Wealth Academy</h2>
    </div>
 

  <!-- New Section After About Us -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Background:</h2>
    <p>
      Reputable stock market firm ShoweWealth Academy, with its headquarters in Bhopal, is committed to busting
       myths about the stock market's resemblance to gambling. ShowerWealth is a company that teaches people about 
       the nuances of the stock market. It is run by Ankush, a seasoned leader with a deep understanding of the market 
       and efficient teaching techniques.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>Objective:</h2>
    <p>
      Creating a static website that provides prospective students with information was the main goal.
       There are several important sections on the website, including the Home, About Us, Gallery, Resources,
        Courses, and Contact pages. It also has a pop-up offering savings on courses and future events. 
        The introduction of a chatbot enables the efficient resolution of customer inquiries, whereas the 
        procedure of opening a Demat account expedites users' entry into trading. Forms are also used to
         effectively collect student data and information.

    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>Defining the Journey:</h2>
    <p>
      Acquiring information and gaining practical experience are essential components of starting a 
      career in the stock market. This path is carefully planned at ShoweWealth Academy to empower
       people at every turn. First, an in-depth understanding of the stock market is acquired through 
       organized classes and online tools. As people continue on, they will see that they can easily open 
       a Demat account and begin trading. Ongoing education and practical experience combine to provide the 
       development required to pursue a profitable stock market career.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>Mission:</h2>
    <p>
      The main goal of ShoweWealth Academy is to give students a thorough understanding of the stock market 
      so they can see a successful future in this exciting industry. The academy seeks to develop people who 
      are not only skilled traders but also competent in negotiating the complexities of the financial market
       through thorough instruction and direction.
 
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>Technologies Used:</h2>
    <p>
      ShoweWealth Academy leveraged Astro.JS, a cutting-edge web framework renowned for its 
      efficiency in content-driven website development. Astro.JS is favored for its rapid loading
       times and robust SEO capabilities, making it an ideal choice for a platform aimed at delivering
        informative content. The website's architecture prioritizes content-driven design, ensuring that 
        users have access to valuable resources and educational materials seamlessly.

    </p>
  </div>

  
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Timeline & Team Size:</h2>
    <p>
      The initiative started with a committed group of six people:



A senior frontend developer, a backend developer, and a junior frontend developer make up the three developers.
One designer is in charge of creating a user interface that is both aesthetically pleasing and easy to use.
One QA Specialist: Making sure the performance and functionality of the website are up to standards.
One Project Manager: Project managers oversee the project's execution and assign team members tasks.
  <br><br>
The project was completed in a short amount of time, taking only 2 weeks to finish. 
    </p>
  </div>

  
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Challenges:</h2>
    <p>
      Throughout the development process, a number of difficulties were faced, including:
Creating a user experience that strikes a balance between ease of use and thorough information, appealing to both experts and students.
Ensuring that the website is responsive to different screen sizes and devices in order to improve user experience.
Adaptability and flexibility are necessary for the team to efficiently handle changing client requests and unstable requirements.
Making educated decisions throughout the project lifecycle by clearly and understandably communicating technical issues to non-technical stakeholders.

    </p>
  </div>

  
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Conclusion:</h2>
    <p>
      The process by which ShoweWealth Academy developed its static website from conception to launch is a 
      prime example of its dedication to both technological innovation and high standards in education. 
      Through the use of state-of-the-art technology and a user-centered approach, the academy hopes to
       enable people to start profitable careers in the stock market. With ongoing education, mentorship, 
       and hands-on training, ShoweWealth Academy is committed to developing the next generation of financial 
       sector professionals.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>

   
   